===Verb===
{{en-verb}}

# To [[drink]] or [[imbibe]] with [[vigour]] or [[relish]]; to drink copiously; to swallow in large [[draught]]s.
#* Shakespeare
#*: '''quaffed''' off the muscadel
#* Milton
#*: They eat, they drink, and in communion sweet / '''Quaff''' immortality and joy.

